{
  "stem": "4361.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we parted, and I said-- and he said that he'll try to arrange it again with this nice detective who took me back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I told my mother and my sister-in-law and the children that he's fine and everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Next thing-- and this was early in May.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No, no, around May 10 or 12, this very policeman walks into the ghetto-- now he knows exactly where we are with my father-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] the grandchildren were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We couldn't get my brother, [NON-ENGLISH] because he was in the other ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We couldn't get him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he gave us an hour, and we were together-- my mother, my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then the detective said, we have to go, that my father has to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we stood, and he said so long to my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they hugged and kissed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They loved each other very much, because my mother-- she fell in love with him when she was very young.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my father was not a very religious-- no, I shouldn't say very religious-- but my father was not a learned man in Talmud.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was a very secular man, and my uncle used to call him the song and dance man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The first lullaby I ever heard, I still weep when I hear that lullaby.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was my father who sang it to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was a very handsome man, a very gentle man, and a very kind man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the story goes that my mother one nice day ran away from home, from one uncle to another.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was the extent of running away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she left a note saying, if you don't let me marry Nandoor, you won't see me ever again.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
